According to Zsoldos' archontology (p. 41.), Stephen ruled [[Slavonia]] at the end of the reign of his father, King Coloman (presumably in 1114). [[User:Borsoka|Borsoka]], do you know any detailed data about this information? --[[User:Norden1990|Norden1990]] ([[User talk:Norden1990|talk]]) 11:45, 6 January 2014 (UTC)

